<img src="/content/dam/research/images/newsletter/2020-07/museum-exhibits-0.jpg" alt="A stack of old black-and-white advertisements for electronics"/>




					 
						<div class="caption richtextContent">
	<p>Professor Ali Mazalek led a team of students in her Synaesthetic Media Lab to explore ways of immersing visitors in the history of 16th century Christian prayer nuts. Photo credit: Synaesthetic Media Lab</p>
</div>
						    
					
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		
